68 is an ideal target for studies of dynamical\nevolution and testing tidal friction theories in hierarchical triple systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2012 07:23:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-02-13"}
