e quantum\nnumbers of these $q\\bar{q}$ mesons in QCD and hadron models in the\nnon-relativistic case, the parity and total angular momentum should be modified\nto $P = (-)^{L + l +1}$ and $\\vec{J} = \\vec{L} + \\vec{l} + \\vec{S}$, where $L$\nis the orbital angular momentum of the $q\\bar{q}$ pair in the meson.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2012 08:08:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 19 Aug 2012 07:02:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 12 Oct 2012 01:17:10 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 14 Jan 2013 10:21:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-30"}
